 within Brisbane: Goodna &amp; Boronia Heights</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Goodna Retirement Village</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>32 Brennan St, Goodna</strong></p>\r\n<p>Oak Tree <a href=\"http://www.oaktreegroup.com.au/goodna-retirement-village.html\" target=\"_blank\">Retirement Village Goodna</a>\r\n is amidst the peaceful surrounds of the Bellbird Park bushlands. Here \r\nyou\'ll enjoy prevailing breezes through the tree tops from our elevated \r\nposition. Conveniently nestled into the neighbourhood we are close to \r\nmedical centres, hospitals, public transport and the Ipswich motorway. \r\nJust a short distance away are parks and retreat areas, restaurants and \r\ncafes and a variety of shopping destinations including Redbank Plains \r\nPlaza and the newly opened Orion Shopping Centre, destined to become one\r\n of Australia\'s largest shopping complexes.</p>','50 Leichhardt St ','Spring Hill','4000',4,11,'Oak Tree Retirement Villages','(07) 3328 4560','','customer@oaktree.com','oaktree.com/index.html','29|permonth','mylvall@yahoo.com',13,0,0,0,'0','1','0'),(4,'Just Garage Doors And Remotes','5','sihenteV1Jf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg,8TW6eTl1Wsf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg,zTKbfQqa1pf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg,KtVKMgpyIJf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg,6blzm3y34Xf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg',3,NULL,NULL,'<p>For sales of Garage Doors and Remote Control systems</p>\r\n<p>For Repairing and&nbsp;Servicing you Garage Doors and Remote Control systems</p>','16 Isobel Street','Clontarf, QLD','4019',4,11,'Just Garage Doors And Remotes','3883 4144 or 0411 868 421','','customer@justgaragedoorsandremotes.com.au','justgaragedoorsandremotes.com.au/','0','mylvall@yahoo.com',3,0,0,0,'1','1','0'),(5,'Qld Movers - Interstate Removalists Brisbane','177,181','VqgmvZl3Enf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg,25udEDzXudf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg',2,NULL,'2012-06-17 06:52:36','<p><strong>Interstate Removalists Queensland</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Qld Movers</strong> have been providing fast, affordable and trouble-free <a href=\"http://www.qldremovals.com.au/removalist-brisbane.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Brisbane removalist</strong></a><strong> services</strong> with the experience and facilities to get your goods to your new home with ease.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Providing Brisbane <a href=\"http://www.qldremovals.com.au/interstate-removals.html\" target=\"_blank\">interstate removals</a></strong>\r\n from Sydney to Cairns, and everywhere in between. We work as \r\nefficiently as possible while still taking care of your valuable \r\nfurniture. We think our personal friendly service is second to none.</p>\r\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://www.qldremovals.com.au/backloading.html\" target=\"_blank\">Brisbane Backloading</a> Services:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Do you only have a small amount of \r\nthings to move? Then you might like to try our backloading service - \r\nwe\'ll add your goods to one of our trucks on its return trip. <br></p>\r\n<p><strong>Packing &amp; Unpacking Service</strong><br></p>\r\n<p><strong>Qld Movers</strong> also provide a complete <strong><a href=\"http://www.qldremovals.com.au/about.html\" target=\"_blank\">packing and unpacking service</a></strong>.\r\n With our very experienced and careful staff we take the worry and \r\nhassle out of packing yourself. This is generally done the day before \r\nthe move. What our staff can do in a day could take you many weekends.</p>','','Brisbane','4000',4,11,'Qld Movers - Interstate Removalists Brisbane','0400 742 949','','info@qldremovals.com.au','qldremovals.com.au/','249|perannum','iankionisala@yahoo.com',5,0,0,0,'1','1','0'),(6,'Signman Says','184','FYHMHCWSXlf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg',2,NULL,'2012-06-17 06:54:17','Signman Says believes your business success relies on clever and \r\neffective advertising through the use of signs, banners, neon signs and \r\nmore. Visit our website for more information.','','Bowen Hills','4006',4,11,'Signman Says','0403 461 252','','customer@signmansays.com.au','','','',4,0,0,0,'1','1','0'),(7,'Aussie Boat Loans - Marine Finance','51','KCQrlSxCpUf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg,MK8H4agIbkf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg,QEVWlQvIRlf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg,SiQD7TZ1dVf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg',2,'2012-06-08 21:36:16','2012-06-17 06:42:56','<p><strong>Aussie Boat Loans</strong> offer low competitive rates for all types of <a href=\"http://www.aussieboatloans.com.au/\">marine finance</a>, boat insurance, hire purchase and leasing, including bad credit boat loans, <a href=\"http://www.aussieboatloans.com.au/business-finance.html\" target=\"_blank\">novated leasing</a>, chattel mortgage and more.<br></p>\r\n<p>Visit our website and apply for a <a href=\"http://www.aussieboatloans.com.au/personal-finance.html\" target=\"_blank\">cheap boat loan</a> online, get a <a href=\"http://www.aussieboatloans.com.au/insurance.html\" target=\"_blank\">marine insurance</a> quote, find your dream boat in the classifieds section, use the <a href=\"http://www.aussieboatloans.com.au/loan-calculator.html\" target=\"_blank\">boat finance calculator</a> for a rough guide to your monthly repayments, or read our finance articles to determine how <strong>Aussie Boat Loans</strong> can best help you. </p>\r\n<p>With offices Australia-wide, and a range of services available, <strong>Aussie Boat Loans</strong> offers a comprehensive financial service for all things marine.</p>','68 Commercial Drive','Shailer Park,','4128',4,11,'Aussie Boat Loans - Marine Finance','1300 769 999','','info@aussieboatloans.com.au','aussieboatloans.com.au/','','',1,0,0,0,'0','2','1'),(44,'Eat Out With Kids','166','7ZnHl9Cspkf528764d624db129b32c21fbca0cb8d6.jpg',1,NULL,NULL,'Vestibulum erat wisi, condimentum sed, commodo vitae, ornare sit amet, \\r\\nwisi. Aenean fermentum, elit eget tincidunt condimentum, eros ipsum \\r\\nrutrum orci, sagittis tempus lacus enim ac dui. Donec non en