een in business for \\r\\nnearly 5 years.<br><br>Your semi permanent eyelash \\r\\nextensions will be individually applied to each of your own lashes. \\r\\nUnlike other companies, a standard set is up to 100 lashes per eye and \\r\\ninclude different lengths, curls and thicknesses to help you achieve the\\r\\n look that best suits you. All done within 1.5 hours! We specialise in \\r\\ncatering for all, from natural to more dramatic!<br><br>Our\\r\\n lashes will look gorgeous for up to 8 weeks, depending on the natural \\r\\ncycle of your own lashes. Following 48 hours from the application of \\r\\nyour lashes you can swim, sweat, cry and expose your new lashes to \\r\\nsteam.<br><br>A beauty treatment that\\\'s more like a pampering, relaxing break away from the stresses and strains of today\\\'s life.<br><br>Dont be fooled by others offering cheap alternatives.</p>','19 Meta Place','Wellington Point','4069',4,11,'Gazelle Botique','0732072273','0418717539','gazelle@gaze.com','gaze.com','premium','kenn_vall@yahoo.com',0,0,0,0,'1','0','0');
