aus-newcastle/archives/587',0,'revision','',0),(588,1,'2012-10-12 17:25:12','2012-10-12 08:25:12','<h3>Newcastle Taxis</h3>\r\nTransfer from the Newcastle Airport with the Newcastle taxis. The taxi rank is adjacent to the arrivals area of the terminal.  There is a dedicated taxi phone located in the arrivals end of the terminal to contact Newcastle Taxis directly and free-of-charge. Phone:  133 300\r\n<h3>Port Stephens Coaches</h3>\r\nNewcastle Airport is serviced by Port Stephens Coaches. A public bus service from Newcastle Airport to Newcastle train station is operated by the Port Stephens Coaches up to 11 times a day.\r\n<strong>Phone:</strong> (02) 4982 2940.\r\n<strong>Website</strong>:<a href=\"http://www.pscoaches.com.au/\" target=\"_blank\"> www.pscoaches.com.au</a>\r\n<h3>Hunter Valley Buses</h3>\r\nHunter Valley Buses operates a public bus service from Newcastle Airport to Raymond Terrace and Stockton.<br />\r\n<strong>Phone:</strong>  (02) 4935 7200\r\n<h3>Newcastle Limousines<em></em></h3>\r\nSpecializing in airport transfers, vineyard tours, weddings, and Sydney transfers, Newcastle Limousines can provide you first class service. With the late model vehicles and professional chauffeurs, Newcastle Limousines can offer you quality luxury transport.\r\n<h3>Adairs Mini Bus and Van Hire</h3>\r\nHigh quality mini buses and vans are provided by Adairs Mini Bus and Van Hire. Wheelchair accessible vehicles are a specialty in Adairs. They also offer Airport transfers to and from Newcastle Airport.\r\n<strong>Phone:</strong> (02) 4340 4030.','More Transfers','','inherit','open','closed','','390-revision-12','','','2012-10-12 17:25:12','2012-10-12 08:25:12','',390,'http://localhost/aus-newcastle/archives/588',0,'revision','',0),(589,1,'2012-10-12 17:16:33','2012-10-12 08:16:33','You can locate the Newcastle Airport Information Services in the arrivals hall at the airport. You can book for your airport transfer at the desk. The Newcastle Airport Information Services